Sunshine Diamond River

Thng tin chnh

  • Sunshine Diamond River
  • Ch u t: Sunshine Group
  • a ch: 422 o Tr, phng Ph Thun, Qun 7, TP.HCM
  • Gi: t 1 - 3 t
Lin h

Gii thiu

D n Sunshine Diamond Riverdo Tp on Sunshine Group lm ch u t, ta lc ngay mt tin ng o Tr, phng Ph Thun, Qun 7, TP. H Ch Minh vi quy m gn 12 hecta cng tng mc vn u t ln n 25,000 t ng. y l khu cn h s hu 3 mt view trc din sng Si Gn cng hn 80% s lng cn h view sng.

V tr d nSunshine Diamond River Qun 7

Ta lc ngay v tr c a, st bn ng ba sng Si Gn giao vi sng ng Nai, cnh cu Ph M, 3 mt k cn ngun nc mang li sinh kh lc ti, khu cn h cao cp v trung tm thng miSunshine Diamond Riverha hn mang n ph qu, an lnh cho nhng ch nhn chn ni y lm chn an c lc nghip.
c bit, d n Sunshine Diamond River cn lin k vi siu d n Saigon Peninsula (Mi n ), y l n by t thc y pht trin, nng cao gi tr ca khu vc o Tr ni ring v khu Nam Si Gn ni chung.

T v tr d n Sunshine Diamond River c th nhanh chng kt ni n:

+ 05 pht n Khu th Ph M Hng

+ 10 pht n Khu th mi Th Thim, Qun 2

+ 15 pht n trung tmQun 1

Trong , bn du thuyn mang n mt loi hnh vn ti kt ni giao thng hon ton mi: h thng du thuyn Azimut ng cp a n c dn t bn du thuyn ni khu ti cc im Water bus dc sng Si Gn kt hp cng h thng t xe Sunshine Cab m bo c dn lun c thoi mi, thun tin trong di chuyn khng cn lo kt xe, nng bc.

H thng Eco System thn thin mi trng bao gm: h thng ti ch nc thi, pin mt tri, h thng thu thp v lc nc ma, nhm mang n li sng XANH THNG MINH ngay trong cn nh.

Tin ch ngoi khu d nSunshine Diamond River

Bn cnh , c dn sinh sng ti d n Sunshine Diamond River cng d dng v thun tin khi kt ni vi tin ch sn c:

+ Trung tm mua sm, siu th, nh hng, caf nh: Big C (cch 300 mt), Crescent Mall (500 mt), Vivo City (10 pht xe my), Lotte Mart, trung tm tic ci Adora, The Coffee House, White House.

+ Trng hc quc t: Hn Quc, i Loan, Nht Bn, Renaissance, trng Nam Si Gn, i hc quc t RMIT, i hc Tn c Thng, i hc Ti Chnh Marketing, trng inh Thin L.

+ Trung tm ti chnh ngn hng: Trung tm ti chnh Ph M Hng, ngn hng ACB, Sacombank, Vietcombank, Vietinbank,

+ Bnh vin quc t Vit Php, bnh vin tim Tm c, bnh vin a Khoa Qun 7

+ Salon Auto nh: Toyota, Mercedes Ben, Kia, Hyundai,

+ Cc ta nh vn phng, trung tm hi ch nh: Petro Tower, Vinamilk, PV Gas, SECC, Maple Tree,

D n Sunshine Diamond River ha hn kin to phong cch sng ngh dng thng minh, hin i, ng thi em n nhng gi tr nh cao v ti to nng lng.
